Package com.example.networkmeup.domain

Class CV

java.lang.Object
com.example.networkmeup.domain.CV
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CV extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a Curriculum Vitae (CV) containing information about education, work experiences, skills, and language knowledge.
